The VIEW a Slide Show menu allows for viewing a show or just one slide.  To
view a show move the cursor to the name of the desired show and press F2 to
view.  If viewing, the F2 Continue key must be pressed between each slide.  To
view one slide, move the cursor to the filename in the directory section and
press F2 to view.




To obtain help for any of the following subjects,  press the function key next
to the desired subject.

        F1  Cancel
        F2  View

        F4  Change Drive


 
        F8  Return to Previous Menu

        F10 Exit from Help

Press F8 to return to the last help screen or F10 to leave the help mode
